Nordic Curls 🎥🙋🏼O.M.G Hamstring killer! Tag a friend!
-
I used the lat pull down machine to set up this exercise. Kneel on and wedge heels under lap bar. Fall forwards in a controlled motion until you reach the bosu ball. Contract hammies & glutes the entire movement and lightly push off bosu ball to assist with bringing yourself back up! 💪🏼
-
This movement forces you to slow down on the negative...constant tension is key! Great isolation exercise as your hamstrings are responsible for holding a majority of your weight!
5 sets of 5 reps 😈 (this is sped up!! back and side view in video)
-
Note: this is an advanced exercise! If you are a beginner I recommend lying hamstring curl with a negative eccentric rep. You could also tie a resistance band to the top of the lat pull down and use for support. ‼
